name.k: リトル ビルダーズ

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 儿童卡车、吊车和挖掘机
子どもたちの大好きなトラック、クレーン、ショベルカー

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 深入地盤施工，一磚一瓦築牆起屋
驾驶重型机械 体验建筑乐趣
化身小小建築家 各式房屋平地起

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Let kids loose in a construction zone where they can place a roof, lay a foundation, paint a house, and more. Children will feel like one of the builders as they operate a crane, cement mixer, and excavator, and they’ll delight in all the surprising little interactions with workers in and around the job sites.
